Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This time crush his head\Ninto the ground, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MOHJI gasps]\N--[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] You're going to\Ngo too? You're wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Are you gonna\Njoin our crew or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we could team up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...in order to achieve\Nour common goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NAll right! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it. [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Epic Showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Swordsman Zoro vs.\NAcrobat Cabaji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'm here to kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I promised\NI would, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just waltz up to\Nme and treat me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Captain Buggy\Nand I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, all I\Nwant is the chart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the treasure then I'm\Nout of here, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here.\NWhy'd you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're outsiders, leave\Nthis to me. [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that I need to be the\None to protect my town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy is my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you\Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you knock out the mayor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the old man had continued\Nto fight he would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to hit him!\NI'm sure we could have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of a more humane way\Nto deal with the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, goes... [inhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the worst thing you\Ncould have said to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NOhh... You damn flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take aim and fire\Nthe Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Luffy, we gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he catch the Buggy Ball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HENCHMEN screaming]\N--[CLOWN HENCHMAN] Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He coulda warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY, HENCHMEN screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell kinda\Nmonster are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you freaked her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI knew that something was weird
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,after you survived\Nthe fight with that lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No human being\Ncan do what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was the\Nballoon inflatey thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you did just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the Gum-Gum Balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you call it,\Njust tell me how you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you,\Nsome kind of freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] How dare you\Ntry to flashily do me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Unreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Using his men as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world\Njust happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI screaming]\NIt's that damn Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!\NWe have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He has Devil Fruit powers, too!\NHe's a rubber person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubber person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains how he bounced\Nthat Buggy Ball back at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] How do you plan\Nto respond to this insult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cabaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too angry to even fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him down, Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did\Nyou do to my Richie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NThis cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I used it as a shield, to keep\Nmy clothes from getting dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NRichie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--[RICHIE whimpers]\N--[MOHJI] Richie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI yells, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NCaptain Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Cabaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] Allow me to\Nrepay their disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. But, make it a\Ngood show for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI gasps]\N--[LUFFY] Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NYou may call me Acrobat Cabaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy's Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pay for your insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'll clash swords with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NIt's an honor, Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As a swordsman myself, I relish\Nthis chance to slay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should get some rest.\NLet me handle this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NJust stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] That's the stab wound\Nthe Captain inflicted on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Arsonist... Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kick you that\Nhard, now did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He fights dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Going after his\Ninjury like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NAcrobat Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder at the Steam Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Acrobat my ass. That's just\Nan ordinary dust cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a disgraceful sight\Nto see a grown man moaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose now you\Ncan see how foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it was to make an enemy\Nof the Buggy Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep fighting with\Nsuch a bad injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hurt so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how he's\Nmanaging to stay in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing\Nthere watching him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna get himself\Nkilled, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro... is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You annoying little bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You havin' fun\Npokin' at my wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Why didn't you\Ndodge his attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Is that enough\Nof a handicap for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And now let me show you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just how superior my\Nskills are to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Zoro! Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, You've made\Na vast error in judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be mocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] My swords aim to\Nbe the world's greatest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to lose even once
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to anyone who calls\Nhimself a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong resolve keeps\Nyou going. But have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wounds as bad as yours
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will be more than\Nenough of an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NFor losing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NTo hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose to someone like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,even with these\Nminimal injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then I don't have a very\Nbright future ahead of me do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NWhy you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stay and watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You pirates can stand\Naround for the rest of time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill each\Nother for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it doesn't matter to me\Nwhether you guys win or lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to swipe their treasure\Nand get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can team up again\Nif we ever get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] Here's a taste of\Nmy ultimate acrobatic move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NAcrobat Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dance of a Hundred\NKamikaze Tops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Luffy and Zoro\Nare completely crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I join up with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell that nothing\Ngood will come of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[banging]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHere we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I steal their\Ntreasure and their chart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Acrobat Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hike in the Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] Fireworks in\Nthe Cool Summer Breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's high!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NSting of the Unicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground-Hugging...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabaji, I'll hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY yelling]\NYou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna fight someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...how about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI giggles]\NLook at all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And every last bit of\Nit is mine! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN] What do you think\Nyou're doin' with our treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of Captain Buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone who gets near\Nthe treasure will, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,more in there [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest just started\Nhurting real bad [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[DRUNK HENCHMAN]\NOoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The chart of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY gumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI laughs]\NI assure you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need my Captain's\Nhelp to finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough... I'm tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI laughing] So you've\Nfinally given up, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say, I'm quite\Nimpressed that you lasted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that long with such\Nserious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI think you misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of watching your\Nboring little side show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry to have\Ndisappointed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My real swordman skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NDie, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NOni...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NGiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the\NBuggy Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...were defeated\Nby petty thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] We aren't petty\Nthieves... [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, I'm goin' to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I scored an impressive\Nhaul from the Buggy Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But hauling treasure is tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's worth\Nthe effort though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I gotta find a\Nway off this island ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NYou guys are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're searching\Nfor the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That's not an easy\Nvoyage, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think\Nthat two halfwits
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the likes of you can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what will you do if,\Nby some miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you manage to make it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on a sightseeing tour\Nor something? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then that would make me God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one who can\Nbe King of the Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and obtain all this\Nworld's treasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's gonna\Nbe me, you got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead and settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Seeing that straw hat\Nbrings back memories of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and that really gets\Nmy blood boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So bring it on,\Nyou wannabe pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You remind me of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn cheeky\Nred-haired pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The red hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you saying you\Nknew my old friend, Shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] That's right.\NI knew Shanks once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that depends, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I do and maybe I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't forget, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not just gonna\Ntell you where he is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,outta the kindness of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work for that info!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll make you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give it your best shot,\Nbut I don't like your chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt rubber can\Nbounce back from a blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NChop-Chop Rice Cracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NCan't move in midair, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHa. Ha. Oh, how interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not so bad either,\Nbut here comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're neat\Nabilities all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but they leave\Nyou wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carve you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good enough, Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Damn, you keep\Nbreaking into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still going at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey, Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass, Pretend\Nyou're still knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get yourself caught\Nin the middle of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no way you'll\Never make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop-Chop Canon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Separate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs] So, runt,\Nyou wanna give up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I not supposed to scratch\Nyour face or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one damages my lucky hat\Nand walks away from it alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This hat is my\Nonly treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyone who so much as lays\Na finger on it is gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a solemn promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised the guy\Nwho gave me this hat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd form a crew and become\Nthe greatest pirate ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't think\Nthat there was anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that could faze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting so\Nupset about a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Hm...It seems that\Nhat has a history to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NIs it really all that special?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nyou should protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gaspsing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBut Shanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sniffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NI'll leave this hat to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It means more to me than\Nanything in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so you better take\Ngood care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS] I want you to bring\Nthis hat back to me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in good condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And only once you've\Nbecome a great pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our promise, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this old, tattered\Nhat a treasure? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure refers to sparkling\Ngold, silver, and jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those things reflect\Ntheir owner's grandeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really consider\Nthis worthless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,dirty straw hat a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to grow\Nup, boy. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shanks gave me that,\NI made a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me that\Nthis used to be Shanks' hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it looked so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He always wore it\Nwhen I knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you and Shanks were members\Nof the same pirate crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, back when we were\Npirates in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We were fellow comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn detestable,\Nred-haired bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks is a much better\Nman then you'll ever be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the right\Nto call him comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you ever\Nbad-mouth him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for my Chop-Chop\NQuick Escape! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to ever mention
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks' name to me\Nagain, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY gasping, coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say whatever the hell\NI want about Shanks! [coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what happened\Nbetween you and Shanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and where can I find him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you tear up my\Ntreasured straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.73,0:22:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NDo you really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one person\Nthat I loathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll curse his name\Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there's\Nbreath in my body, Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.91,0:24:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGet ready, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.83,0:24:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYeah! Get him, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou'll pay for damaging
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.96,0:24:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the hat that Shanks\Nentrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NEnough talk, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.13,0:24:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish this clown and\Nprotect my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh? That doesn't sound right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIt's basically the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.30,0:24:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is the Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Fruit Power Showdown!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.47,0:24:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

